                {
                    "subtitle": "Was Placement Successful?",
                    "components": [
                        {
                            "type": "text-paragraph",
                            "text": "Students will usually have a debriefing session and be encouraged to reflect on their placement. It is also good practice for staff to reflect on their practice and articulate things that went really well on this cycle and how the learning can be used by the team when preparing for other placements."
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "text-paragraph",
                            "text": "It may also be helpful to collate feedback from placement sites and educators or mentors."
